### Sizing formula

```
maxW = screenW * 0.90
maxH = (screenH - safeInsets - HUD_BAR_HEIGHT) * 0.85
courtW = maxW; courtH = courtW / (9/16)
if courtH > maxH тЖТ courtH = maxH; courtW = courtH * (9/16)
```

