## Phase5 тАФ Flexible Orientation Transitions тЬЕ

**Goal:** Correct behavior when user rotates between screens; stable gameplay during a match.

### Decision (revised)

Initial approach: debounced mid-game restart (`resetActiveGame`) on orientation change. **Device QA failed** тАФ paddles kept portrait Y positions in landscape, ball could disappear, layout loops caused "Maximum update depth exceeded".

**Current approach:** Lock orientation for the duration of an active match. Free rotation on intro and win screens only.

### Intro / win rotation flow

```
orientation change (!gameStarted || winner !== null)
  тЖТ useLayoutEffect:
      isPortraitSV updated
      setCourtBounds(null)   // avoid stale overlay frame
  тЖТ court onLayout:
      updateCourtBounds (guarded)
      syncCourtMetrics + positionPaddles
  тЖТ portrait: overlay reframes via CourtOverlayFrame + courtBounds
  тЖТ landscape: fullScreenOverlay on playArea (centered Start/Win/Pause; compact layout)
  тЖТ court key={portrait|landscape} forces remeasure on orientation flip
```

### Active play flow

```
gameStarted && !winner
  тЖТ lockedGameplayPortrait set in startGame / playAgain
  тЖТ useGameplayOrientationLock(lockedPortrait):
      lockAsync(PORTRAIT_UP | LANDSCAPE)
      accelerometer baseline tilt (normalized gravity angle via expo-sensors)
      + Dimensions / ScreenOrientation listeners as fallback
  тЖТ on physical rotate (~32┬░ from baseline) or UI dimension mismatch:
      RotationLockedBanner (4s, safe-area bottom padding)
      isPaused = true (auto-resume when banner dismisses)
      haptic warning; re-lock orientation
  тЖТ on unlock: intro screen or win overlay
```

### Done

- [x] Layout switch without remounting `GameScreen`
- [x] `CourtOverlayFrame` тАФ portrait start/win/pause overlays match court bounds
- [x] Landscape menus use `fullScreenOverlay` (not court bounds тАФ fixes intro rotate layout)
- [x] `StartOverlay` / `WinOverlay` / `PauseOverlay` extracted; `compact` prop for landscape
- [x] Portrait HUD visible during overlays (not covered)
- [x] `courtBounds` tracked from court `onLayout`; cleared on orientation change
- [x] `lockedGameplayPortrait` captured at `startGame` / `playAgain`; cleared when match ends
- [x] Court `key={portrait|landscape}` forces layout remeasure on orientation flip
- [x] Gameplay entities hidden under overlays (no paddle/scoreboard bleed-through)
- [x] `beginMatch()` тАФ single start/play-again path; paddle heights set before `positionPaddles()`; ball always launched after `ensurePrimaryBall()` + `bumpBalls()`
- [x] **Missing ball on start fix** тАФ sync `gameStartedRef` immediately; `handleLayout` treats `isPlaying` as active match (prevents pre-game branch from resetting paddles while ball attaches); portrait uses `layoutConfig.portraitCourtSize` fallback; landscape defers via `pendingServeSideRef` until first `onLayout`
- [x] Mid-game orientation **lock** replaces debounced restart
- [x] `RotationLockedBanner` for rotation-blocked feedback (replaces `GameToast`)
- [x] `expo-sensors` accelerometer тАФ normalized gravity tilt detect (works in g and m/s┬▓)
